<head>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/static/css/product/prodDetail.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/static/css/layouts/style.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
          integrity="sha384-EVSTQN3/azprG1Anm3QDgpJLIm9Nao0Yz1ztcQTwFspd3yD65VohhpuuCOmLASjC" crossorigin="anonymous" />
</head>
<body>
{{#product}}
<header>
    <div class="cate-info">
        {{prod_cate}} >> {{prod_decate}}
    </div>
    <hr>
</header>
<nav>
{{#productimage}}
    <div id="carouselExampleControls" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
        <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img src="/static/images/Product/{{image_link}}" class="prod-image" alt="...">
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="/static/images/Product/{{image_link2}}" class="prod-image" alt="...">
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="/static/images/Product/{{image_link3}}" class="prod-image" alt="...">
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="/static/images/Product/{{image_link4}}" class="prod-image" alt="...">
            </div>
        </div>
        <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleControls"
                data-bs-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
        </button>
        <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleControls"
                data-bs-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
        </button>
    </div>
{{/productimage}}
</nav>
<section>
    <div class="prod-info">
        <div class="prod-score">
            <h3>평점</h3>
            <div class="prod-score-text">
                <p>4</p>
            </div>
            <div class="like"><button>좋아요</button></div>
        </div>
        <div class="prod-name">
            <h3>상품명</h3>
            <div class="prod-name-text">
                <p>{{prod_name}}</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="prod-price">
            <h3>판매가</h3>
            <div class="prod-price-text">
                <p>{{prod_price}}</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="prod-discount-price">
            <h3>할인가</h3>
            <div class="prod-discount-text">
                <p>{{prod_discount_price}}</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="prod-diliver-price">
            <h3>배송비</h3>
            <div class="prod-diliver-text">
                <p>{{diliver_price}}</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="prod-size">
            <h3>사이즈</h3>
            <div class="prod-size-text">
                <select class="size-option">
                    <option>{{prod_XS}}</option>
                    <option>{{prod_S}}</option>
                    <option>{{prod_M}}</option>
                    <option>{{prod_L}}</option>
                    <option>{{prod_XL}}</option>
                </select>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="prod-buy-button">
            <button type="submit" class="basket-button">장바구니</button>
            <button type="submit" class="buy-button">바로결제</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<hr>
<main>
    <div class="prod-detail-image-title">
        <h3 style="color: aqua;">상품 상세이미지</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="prod-detail-image-form">
        {{#productdeimage}}
        <div class="prod-detail-image">
            <img src="/static/images/Product/{{deimage_link}}" class="detail-image">
        </div>
        <div class="prod-detail-image">
            <img src="/static/images/Product/{{deimage_link2}}" class="detail-image">
        </div>
        <div class="prod-detail-image">
            <img src="/static/images/Product/{{deimage_link3}}" class="detail-image">
        </div>
        <div class="prod-detail-image">
            <img src="/static/images/Product/{{deimage_link4}}" class="detail-image">
        </div>
        <div class="prod-detail-image">
            <img src="/static/images/Product/{{deimage_link5}}" class="detail-image">
        </div>
        {{/productdeimage}}
    </div>
    <div class="prod-detail-info">
        <div>상품상태: <input type="text" placeholder="새 재품" readonly></div><br>
        <div class="prod-info-text">원산지 : <input type="text" placeholder="한국" readonly></div><br>
        <div class="prod-info-text">출고지 : <input type="text" placeholder="서울" readonly></div><br>
        <div>판매형태 :<input type="text" placeholder="도매" readonly></div>
    </div>
   {{/product}}
    <hr>
    <div class="review-title">
        <h2>리뷰</h2>
        <div>
            <h3>리뷰갯수: <b>3</b>개</h3>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="review-form">
        <div class="review-info-form">
            <h3>평점 : 4</h3>
            <h3>유저닉네임</h3>
            <h3>사이즈 : L</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="review-date">
            <h3>2017-08-28</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="review-image-form">
            <img src="/image/image1.jfif" class="review-image">
        </div>
        <div class="review-content">
            <p>약간 루즈핏이에여 색감자체는 예쁘게 잘 나왔고 182cm 에 70kg인데 라지 사이즈 입으면 적당합니다</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="review-form">
        <div class="review-info-form">
            <h3>평점 : 4</h3>
            <h3>유저닉네임</h3>
            <h3>사이즈 : M</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="review-date">
            <h3>2017-08-28</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="review-image-form">
            <img src="/image/image1.jfif" class="review-image">
        </div>
        <div class="review-content">
            <p>생각보다 사이즈가 크게나와요 땅달보들은 S사야 할것같아요</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="review-form">
        <div class="review-info-form">
            <h3>평점 : 4</h3>
            <h3>유저닉네임</h3>
            <h3>사이즈 : M</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="review-date">
            <h3>2017-08-28</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="review-image-form">
            <img src="/image/image1.jfif" class="review-image">
        </div>
        <div class="review-content">
            <p>좋아요</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-MrcW6ZMFYlzcLA8Nl+NtUVF0sA7MsXsP1UyJoMp4YLEuNSfAP+JcXn/tWtIaxVXM" crossorigin="anonymous">
</script>
</body>
</html>